Do you want the privacy of your colleagues?
There are no good ways to stop potions that spread.
Who did what, with whom?
Or why?
Don’t tell everyone your information (suppositions) about the privacy of your colleagues!
If a colleague shares his intimate secrets with you, don’t abuse his trust!
Bury the information you share and don’t discuss it with your colleagues in their absence even if your colleagues are also aware of it.
Are you declaring yourself sick for no good reason?
