Peace, enrichment, telephone
You're diving into your work, but the wealth of your co-workers is getting you out of it?
Did you become, unwittingly, a witness to a phone conversation that you would have done better not to listen to?
Don’t bother your colleagues with sneezing, chanting, loud conversations (which you lead above their heads), kicks, big words, or loud-voiced dissatisfaction.
