Are you accusing others of a fault?
If your work is not done for the set time, you forget to send an important email or message, don’t blame anyone for this forget!
Do not put it on the account of any chaos in the office or your noisy colleagues!
Recognize it if you made a mistake and if it presented inconveniences to others, fix the mistake!
Ask how you could fix your fault, fix negligence!
Do you feel too much at home in the office?
Putting on a jogging and socks is comfortable at home but they are not suitable for the office!
Do not put comfortable jogging even if your function allows it!
Don’t forget, respect your colleagues and yourself by dressing properly, and if your function requires it by putting on nice and elegant clothes, to go to work!
